  "remarks": "As of mid-2014, Syria-based senior military commander and shura council\nmember of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant, listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (AQI)\n(QDe.115). Led approximately 1,000 foreign fighters for ISIL and committed a number of\nattacks in northern Syria.\nReview pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
